data.description: Worried about high-interest rates?  This home has an assumable mortgage at 4%.  Completely renovated in 2015, this house has been made a home, now it’s time to make it yours! This home features a more open floor plan, updated kitchen, flooring, and bathrooms. The expanded kitchen has shaker-style cabinetry, stone backsplash, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and lots of storage. The flooring has distressed barn wood tile throughout the foyer, kitchen, and laundry area, hardwood in the living and dining room, carpet on the upper level, and tile in the bathrooms and basement. The finished basement provides plenty of extra living space, it has been utilized as a playroom and office space; however, can be utilized as you see fit. The AC, heater, and HWH were all installed during the renovation. The roof was installed in 2020 and the windows in 2021 (with the exception of the kitchen, basement, and sliding back door which were all installed during the 2015 renovation). Window warranty information is attached for the windows installed in 2021. This home has gone solar! Don’t miss your opportunity to utilize sun power to help keep expenses down! A binder is available during showings to get a glimpse of the monthly electrical expenses the homeowners have had over the last 12 months. Book your showing today! This is one you’re not going to want to miss!!
